<li><span id="CITEREFWilliams1990">Williams, John B. 1990. <i>Image Clarity: High-Resolution Photography</i>. Boston: Focal Press.</span> <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0240800338" class="internal">ISBN 0-240-80033-8</a></li>
